      <h1>How B2B Companies Simplify Complex Products with Explainer Videos</h1>
      <p class="lead">Discover how explainer videos simplify complex ideas, boost engagement, and accelerate B2B decision-making.</p>
      <p class="post-meta"><span>Sofia Treviño</span> <span>·</span> <span>July 5, 2024</span> <span>·</span> <span>Updated March 25, 2025</span></p>
